---
import MainLayout from '../layouts/MainLayout.astro';
import LegacyHeader from '../components/LegacyHeader.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
import ContactSection from '../components/ContactSection.astro';
import Hero from '../components/Hero.astro';
import ButtonPrimary from '../components/ButtonPrimary.astro';
import ButtonSecondary from '../components/ButtonSecondary.astro';
---

<MainLayout title="Backlink SEO Services Philippines - Bright Forge SEO" description="Boost your online presence with our expert backlink SEO services in the Philippines. Quality backlink strategies to elevate your search rankings.">
  <LegacyHeader slot="header" />

  <!-- Hero Section -->
  <Hero
    badgeIcon="fas fa-link"
    badgeText="Backlink SEO Specialists"
    title="Boost Your Online Presence with Expert Backlink SEO Services in the Philippines"
    breadcrumbCurrent="Backlink SEO Services Philippines"
  >
    <Fragment slot="story">
      <p>When it comes to SEO, backlinks are more than just a nice-to-have—they're a cornerstone of successful search engine optimisation. At Bright Forge SEO, we understand how powerful backlinks can be in propelling your website to the top of Google's search results.</p>
      <p>If you've ever tried to get your website to rank higher on Google, you've probably heard of backlinks. But why are they so critical? Backlinks, essentially links from other websites pointing to yours, act like votes of confidence for your site. The more quality backlinks you have, the more Google sees your site as trustworthy and authoritative.</p>
    </Fragment>

    <Fragment slot="actions">
      <ButtonPrimary href="/contact/" text="Get Your Free Backlink Audit" />
      <ButtonSecondary href="#services" text="See Our Process" />
    </Fragment>

    <Fragment slot="visual">
      <div class="hero-image-container">
        <div class="backlink-icon-grid">
          <div class="backlink-icon"><i class="fas fa-link"></i></div>
          <div class="backlink-icon"><i class="fas fa-globe"></i></div>
          <div class="backlink-icon"><i class="fas fa-chart-line"></i></div>
          <div class="backlink-icon"><i class="fas fa-handshake"></i></div>
          <div class="backlink-icon"><i class="fas fa-star"></i></div>
          <div class="backlink-icon"><i class="fas fa-trophy"></i></div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </Fragment>
  </Hero>

  <!-- Why Backlinks Matter Section -->
  <section class="why-backlinks-section">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4">
      <div class="section-header">
        <h2>Why Are <span>Backlinks</span> So Important?</h2>
      </div>

      <div class="content-explanation">
        <div class="content-card">
          <div class="content-icon">
            <i class="fas fa-link"></i>
          </div>
          <div class="content-text">
            <p>Backlinks act like votes of confidence for your site. The more quality backlinks you have, the more Google sees your site as trustworthy and authoritative. It's like having a bunch of positive reviews from reputable sources!</p>

            <p>However, not all backlinks are created equal. Quality matters more than quantity. You want backlinks from sites that are relevant, authoritative, and trustworthy. Our Backlink SEO Services focus on acquiring the highest quality links for your website to improve your search engine visibility.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Core Backlink Services Section -->
  <section id="services" class="services-section-new">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4">
      <div class="services-layout">
        <div class="services-content">
          <h2>Our Backlink Building <span>Services</span></h2>

          <div class="service-list">
            <div class="service-item">
              <h3>Strategic Link Prospecting</h3>
              <p>We identify high-authority, relevant websites in your industry and analyze competitor backlink profiles to uncover valuable link opportunities that will boost your domain authority.</p>
            </div>

            <div class="service-item">
              <h3>White-Hat Link Building</h3>
              <p>Ethical outreach campaigns, guest posting on authoritative sites, and content marketing strategies that naturally attract quality backlinks without risking search engine penalties.</p>
            </div>

            <div class="service-item">
              <h3>Broken Link Reclamation</h3>
              <p>We find broken backlinks pointing to your site, recover lost link equity, and identify broken links on relevant sites where we can offer your content as a replacement.</p>
            </div>

            <div class="service-item">
              <h3>Link Profile Management</h3>
              <p>Continuous monitoring of your backlink profile, toxic link identification and disavowal, and regular reporting on link acquisition progress and impact on rankings.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="services-visual">
          <div class="visual-card">
            <div class="visual-icon">
              <i class="fas fa-link"></i>
            </div>
            <h3>Quality Links Built</h3>
            <p class="visual-stat">250+</p>
            <p class="visual-label">High-Quality Backlinks Per Campaign</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Process Section -->
  <section class="process-section">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4">
      <div class="process-header">
        <h2>Our Backlink Building <span>Process</span></h2>
        <p>We follow a strategic approach to build high-quality backlinks that improve your search rankings and drive sustainable results.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="process-grid">
        <div class="process-box orange-bg">
          <div class="process-box-icon">
            <i class="fas fa-search"></i>
          </div>
          <h3>Research & Analysis</h3>
          <p>We analyze your website and competitors to identify link opportunities and conduct a comprehensive backlink audit to assess your current link profile.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="process-box white-bg">
          <div class="process-box-icon">
            <i class="fas fa-bullseye"></i>
          </div>
          <h3>Target Identification</h3>
          <p>We focus on acquiring backlinks from reputable, industry-relevant websites that will provide the most value for your SEO efforts.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="process-box orange-bg">
          <div class="process-box-icon">
            <i class="fas fa-handshake"></i>
          </div>
          <h3>Outreach Campaigns</h3>
          <p>We reach out to webmasters and bloggers with personalized messages, building authentic relationships that result in natural, credible backlinks.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="process-box white-bg">
          <div class="process-box-icon">
            <i class="fas fa-file-alt"></i>
          </div>
          <h3>Content Creation</h3>
          <p>We create shareable, engaging content that naturally attracts backlinks—from blog posts to infographics and resource guides.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="process-box orange-bg">
          <div class="process-box-icon">
            <i class="fas fa-shield-alt"></i>
          </div>
          <h3>Quality Assurance</h3>
          <p>Every backlink is vetted for quality and relevance. We use only white-hat SEO techniques that comply with Google's guidelines.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="process-box white-bg">
          <div class="process-box-icon">
            <i class="fas fa-chart-bar"></i>
          </div>
          <h3>Monitoring & Reporting</h3>
          <p>We continuously monitor your backlink profile and provide detailed reports so you can track progress and see real results.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Benefits Section -->
  <section class="benefits-section">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4">
      <div class="benefits-header">
        <h2>The Benefits of Quality <span>Backlinks</span></h2>
        <p>Strategic backlink building delivers lasting advantages for your website's authority and search performance.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="benefits-layout">
        <div class="benefits-visual">
          <img
            src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1460925895917-afdab827c52f?w=800&q=80"
            alt="SEO analytics and backlink analysis dashboard"
            class="benefits-image"
          />
        </div>

        <div class="benefits-grid">
          <div class="benefit-card">
            <div class="benefit-icon">
              <i class="fas fa-chart-line"></i>
            </div>
            <h3>Higher Rankings</h3>
            <p>Quality backlinks signal trust to search engines, helping your website rank higher for competitive keywords and drive more organic traffic.</p>
          </div>

          <div class="benefit-card">
            <div class="benefit-icon">
              <i class="fas fa-trophy"></i>
            </div>
            <h3>Increased Authority</h3>
            <p>Build domain authority and establish your website as a trusted resource in your industry through strategic link acquisition.</p>
          </div>

          <div class="benefit-card">
            <div class="benefit-icon">
              <i class="fas fa-users"></i>
            </div>
            <h3>Referral Traffic</h3>
            <p>Quality backlinks don't just boost SEO—they drive targeted referral traffic from relevant websites to your content.</p>
          </div>

          <div class="benefit-card">
            <div class="benefit-icon">
              <i class="fas fa-shield-alt"></i>
            </div>
            <h3>Long-Term Results</h3>
            <p>Our white-hat approach ensures sustainable growth that will keep your website ranking well without risking search engine penalties.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Why Choose Us Section -->
  <section class="why-choose-us">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4">
      <div class="section-header">
        <h2>Why Choose <span>Bright Forge SEO</span> for Backlink Services?</h2>
        <p>Here's what makes us stand out in the world of Backlink SEO:</p>
      </div>

      <div class="features-grid">
        <div class="feature-card">
          <div class="feature-icon">
            <i class="fas fa-award"></i>
          </div>
          <h3>Experience You Can Trust</h3>
          <p>With years of experience in the SEO industry, we have a proven track record of improving search engine rankings for businesses across various sectors. We're a trusted <a href="/">SEO agency</a> in the Philippines that takes a hands-on approach to building your online authority.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="feature-card">
          <div class="feature-icon">
            <i class="fas fa-bullseye"></i>
          </div>
          <h3>Tailored Link Building Strategies</h3>
          <p>Every business is unique, so why should your link-building strategy be the same as everyone else's? We tailor our approach based on your specific needs, goals, and industry.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="feature-card">
          <div class="feature-icon">
            <i class="fas fa-eye"></i>
          </div>
          <h3>Transparency and Integrity</h3>
          <p>We believe in building trust, not just links. From day one, we ensure you're fully aware of the steps we're taking and the progress we're making. Our detailed reports give you full visibility into the work we're doing for you.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="feature-card">
          <div class="feature-icon">
            <i class="fas fa-chart-line"></i>
          </div>
          <h3>Sustainable Long-Term Results</h3>
          <p>We don't just aim for quick wins. Our backlink services are designed to provide sustainable growth that will keep your website ranking well in the long term, without risking penalties from search engines.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="feature-card">
          <div class="feature-icon">
            <i class="fas fa-shield-alt"></i>
          </div>
          <h3>Ethical White-Hat Practices</h3>
          <p>We take pride in using ethical SEO strategies. Our backlink-building methods comply with Google's guidelines, meaning you can rest easy knowing your SEO efforts are in safe hands.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- FAQ Section -->
  <section class="faq-section">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4">
      <div class="section-header">
        <h2>Frequently Asked Questions About <span>Backlink SEO</span></h2>
        <p>Got questions about our backlink SEO services? We've got answers.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="faq-container">
        <div class="faq-item">
          <div class="faq-question" onclick="toggleFAQ(this)">
            <h3>What is backlink SEO?</h3>
            <i class="fas fa-chevron-down"></i>
          </div>
          <div class="faq-answer">
            <p>Backlink SEO is the process of acquiring backlinks from other websites to improve your own site's search engine rankings. The goal is to build an authoritative backlink profile that signals trust to search engines like Google.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="faq-item">
          <div class="faq-question" onclick="toggleFAQ(this)">
            <h3>How long does it take to see results from backlinks?</h3>
            <i class="fas fa-chevron-down"></i>
          </div>
          <div class="faq-answer">
            <p>While every website is different, most businesses see noticeable improvements in their rankings within 3-6 months of implementing a strategic backlink SEO campaign.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="faq-item">
          <div class="faq-question" onclick="toggleFAQ(this)">
            <h3>Are all backlinks the same?</h3>
            <i class="fas fa-chevron-down"></i>
          </div>
          <div class="faq-answer">
            <p>No! The quality of a backlink is far more important than the quantity. A link from a reputable, industry-relevant site is far more valuable than dozens of links from low-quality websites.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="faq-item">
          <div class="faq-question" onclick="toggleFAQ(this)">
            <h3>How do you choose the right websites for backlinks?</h3>
            <i class="fas fa-chevron-down"></i>
          </div>
          <div class="faq-answer">
            <p>We evaluate sites based on their domain authority, relevance to your industry, and overall trustworthiness. We focus on websites that align with your brand and have a positive reputation.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <ContactSection />
  <Footer slot="footer" />
</MainLayout>

<style>
/* Backlink Icon Grid (used in Hero visual slot) */
.hero-image-container {
  position: relative;
  width: 100%;
  max-width: 500px;
}

.backlink-icon-grid {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
  gap: 2rem;
  padding: 2rem;
}

.backlink-icon {
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  justify-content: center;
  width: 80px;
  height: 80px;
  background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.15);
  backdrop-filter: blur(20px);
  border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.2);
  border-radius: 20px;
  color: white;
  font-size: 2rem;
  transition: all 0.3s ease;
  animation: float 4s ease-in-out infinite;
}

@keyframes float {
  0%, 100% { transform: translateY(0px); }
  50% { transform: translateY(-10px); }
}

.backlink-icon:nth-child(odd) {
  animation-delay: 1s;
}

.backlink-icon:nth-child(even) {
  animation-delay: 2s;
}

.backlink-icon:hover {
  transform: translateY(-5px) scale(1.05);
  background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.25);
  border-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.4);
}

@media (max-width: 1024px) {
  .backlink-icon-grid {
    grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
    gap: 1.5rem;
  }
}

@media (max-width: 768px) {
  .backlink-icon-grid {
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    gap: 1rem;
  }

  .backlink-icon {
    width: 60px;
    height: 60px;
    font-size: 1.5rem;
  }
}

